1. The flexibility of the glass screen protector is the same as the plastic material, is it tempered glass or plastic? This screen protector is a real tempered glass. The plastic flexibility is the exact reason why we call it tempered glass screen protector. Tempered glass is a type of safety glass that is stronger than ordinary glass. 2. It cannot be seen from the appearance that it is glass or plastic. As a customer, what can we do to identify it? There is an easy, quick, cost-effective way to test it yourself, and it's very accurate. Most plastics have a melting point between 160 and 210 degrees Celsius, and glass materials are at least over 1400 degrees Celsius, so is there a lighter around? 3. Does it come with a cleaning wipe to use prior to placing on the phone? Yes,the package includes: 6*Guide Stickers, 3*Wet Wipe & 1*Dry Wipe, 3*Dust Absorber 4.How can I remove bubbles? Use the kit in the package to clean the screen before placing the screen protector.If there are bubbles, try to gently press the bubbles with your finger or with a ruler,but the screen surface needs a thin cloth pad to avoid scratching the protector. 5.How can I remove a cracked glass screen protector? Lift the screen protector with the card from any corner of the screen protector, then hold the corner and remove slowly. (If you find CHIP or CRACK on the screen protector, for your safety, please wear gloves when removing the screen protector.)

reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Great Protection for My iPhone 14 Pro!
reviews.reviewText: I recently purchased the Ailun 3 Pack Screen Protector for iPhone 14 Pro, and I must say, I am highly impressed with its performance. Its case-friendly design ensures compatibility with most phone cases, which is a huge plus for me as I like to change my phone case frequently.The 9H hardness of this screen protector provides exceptional protection against scratches, scuffs, and accidental drops. I have been using it for a few weeks now, and my iPhone's screen remains flawless. The high-definition clarity of the film maintains the original screen quality, allowing me to enjoy vibrant colors and sharp images.One of the standout features of this product is the camera lens protector. It perfectly covers the camera lens, ensuring that it remains scratch-free and protected from dust and fingerprints. The sensor protection is an added bonus, as it safeguards my iPhone's sensors from any potential damage.In terms of durability, the Ailun screen protector has exceeded my expectations. The oleophobic coating effectively repels fingerprints and smudges, keeping my screen clean and clear at all times.Overall, I am extremely satisfied with the Ailun 3 Pack Screen Protector for iPhone 14 Pro. It offers excellent protection, maintains the original screen quality, and is incredibly easy to install. Considering the reasonable price and the inclusion of camera lens and sensor protection, this product is a fantastic value for money. reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on October 16, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 4.0 out of 5 stars A Balance of Clarity and Protection
reviews.reviewText: I recently purchased the Ailun 2Pack Privacy Screen Protector for my new iPhone 14 Plus, and I must say it strikes a commendable balance between ease of installation and the delicate nature of the material.The package includes not only two privacy screen protectors but also two camera lens protectors, which is a thoughtful addition. The privacy feature is a significant plus for those of us who value our personal space. It effectively limits the viewing angles, ensuring that my screen content stays my own.Installation was a breeze, thanks to the detailed instructions provided. The protector adhered seamlessly to my screen, and it's impressively case-friendly, fitting snugly without any compatibility issues.One thing to bear in mind, however, is that this screen protector, while providing excellent privacy features, is a bit on the delicate side. I discovered it's easy to crack, so handling it with care during installation and everyday use is crucial.The 9H hardness offers substantial protection against scratches and scuffs, which is always a priority for any screen protector. The HD clarity is commendable, preserving the vibrant display of my iPhone 14 Plus without any discernible loss in visual quality.In terms of design, the black border adds a sleek touch to the overall look. It seamlessly integrates with my phone's aesthetics.In summary, the Ailun Privacy Screen Protector for iPhone 14 Plus is a solid choice for those seeking a blend of privacy and protection. It excels in its privacy features, maintains crystal clear display quality, and is hassle-free to install. Just exercise caution as it's more prone to cracking compared to some other protectors.Pros:- Effortless installation- Effective privacy features- Inclusion of camera lens protectors- Case-friendly design- Impressive scratch resistanceCons:- Relatively delicate material, prone to crackingOverall, I'm somewhat pleased with my purchase, knowing that my iPhone 14 Plus is now equipped with a screen protector that balances privacy and protection effectively. However, I wish it wasn’t so delicate.
